  "body": "I just imported one of my tests account and Status did its recovery. While processing, my screen looked like this:\r\n\r\n![Screenshot from 2023-06-06 14-41-12](https://github.com/status-im/status-desktop/assets/445106/9ff871ee-31b1-4a13-aaf2-efb529ed0266)\r\n\r\nThe bottom part is cut off. I do realize that this is due to the height of my window, but since the pure content does fit into the height, I'd expect it to be vertically centered regardless.",
